sellerCard.description:
Hi, I'm Saeed ullah, a Certified Web Application Developer with over 5 years of experience of Php website development. I specialized in HTML, PHP, JavaScript, Bootstrap, Web, and CSS. I create websites from scratch, ensuring they're SEO-friendly and optimized. 

My skills include PHP for Back-end Web development, Bootstrap for Front-end Web Development and Full Stack Web development. I'm also experienced in deploying websites on AWS and Digital Ocean. I'm dedicated to delivering user-friendly and technically sound web solutions.

description.content:
Hello Everyone! I am a PHP developer with extensive experience developing dynamic, efficient web applications.


If you select me to develop your project, I will not consider you as my boss but as a partner, and I will build a website as if it were my own. 

 

As a PHP Developer, I have completed several projects and gained popularity as the go-to person for crafting web experiences that flow perfectly. I understand that every client is unique and tailor my expertise to meet your needs.


I use the following stack technologies:


  • HTML
  • PHP
  • JavaScript
  • CSS


What I offer?


  • SEO-friendly, optimized code
  • Google Map API integration
  • Twilio for SMS integration
  • Bug fixing and debugging in PHP laravel
  • PHP website development from scratch
  • AWS/Digital Ocean Deployment


Why choose me?


  • 100% Satisfaction Guaranteed
  • Get Your Money Back if You're Not Satisfied
  • Well-Structured Code for Optimal Performance
  • Post Project Support & Maintenance
  • Budget friendly


It's time to build something amazing together! Message and get your dream website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Where can I find PHP developers with experience building web applications?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You are at the right Gig; I am an experienced PHP developer always ready to assist you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What traits and requirements should I consider when hiring a PHP developer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: When hiring a PHP Developer, always see the experience of that professional, expertise in database skills, familiarity with JavaScript and CSS, API Integration, testing skills and portfolio.

questionsAndAnswers.question: In what ways can a PHP developer help ensure the success of my web app?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Proficient PHP developers ensure success in Laravel web app development by applying professional larval framework knowledge, optimizing performance levels, and securing vulnerabilities against malware attacks and spy bots.

questionsAndAnswers.question: As a PHP developer, how much will you charge?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: As a Laravel or PHP developer, I will charge as per the project, but you do not have to worry; I will provide you with an economical quote with the best service possible.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can I trust you to build my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: As I stated, I offer a 100% money-back guarantee; if you do not like my work, I will return your hard-earned money to you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why should I pay to a PHP Developer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You might think it will be a lot to invest in hiring a PHP Developer, but you need a fantastic website and mobile application in today's market. Therefore, a PHP developer can assist you in reaching out to your potential clients.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I need urgent work done by a PHP Developer. Can you complete tasks on time?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No matter what your project is, it will always be delivered on time, and as for urgency, I charge a little bit higher but provide you the best service and 100% on time.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have been scammed by a PHP Developer before; how can I trust you?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have been in this business for several years, and you can ask for my portfolio; I will be more than happy to share it with you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you build my website during the holidays?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For me, your happiness and mental peace are of utmost importance; if you want a task done on vacation, I will do my best to complete it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you handle a situation where a task appears simple initially but later proves to be more complex?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If a task initially seems straightforward but later uncovers additional complexities, I will promptly communicate this. Subsequently, we can engage in discussions to determine the optimal approach, which might include adjusting the project scope, or budget to align with the updated requirements.
